    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> beef mince</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>then<strong> </strong>cook for 4-5 min or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
